
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.0 (2011-01-10)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- first release

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.1.0 (2011-01-17)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- fixed a bug in large file put/get/cat operations
- put command: deviceFilename is now optional (defaults to filename of 
  localFilepath)
- get command: localFilepath is now optional (defaults to deviceFilename)
- reduced sleeptime to speed up large file transfers
- tested on linux (debian 5.0 lenny)
- added --flowcontrol commandline parameter (needed for linux)
- added sleep command (useful for scripting)
- added --wait commandline parameter (wait for modem to become ready)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.2.0 (2011-01-18)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- added AT command support (look at sample cmd.txt to see how it's done)


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.3.0 (2011-01-22)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- added command line switches (-at and -ot) for AT and OBEX command timeouts

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.4.0 (2011-09-02)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- added 'getd' command provided by Thomas Martinec 
- when device inited, obex mode is forcefully opened (some devices need this)
  
